{
  "stem": "14897.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there would be places, for example, where you could have the top would be outside of the ghetto, and the lower floor would be in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember there was one drain pipe like that, rain, for rain.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was used to pour stuff-- pour milk, and then they would to dry it, and they would pour rice, or they would pour flour, and so on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were very ingenious method of smuggling food into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father was again, of course, working as a doctor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he was making a living of sorts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were much better off than many people in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You have to realize, the ghetto of Warsaw housed about half a million people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So it's-- was all crowded into a fairly small area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So living space was at a premium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And people who had apartments by now shared them with relatives, with friends, with-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, rented rooms and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the name of the street where we stayed during the war was called Nalewki, N-A-L-E-W-K-I.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do have a map of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't know if you can see it at the moment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe I'll show it to you a little later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] life for me again became-- it's hard to say normal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you know, under any circumstances, things become, when they go on like that, they become the norm for you at the time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you adjust, to some extent, to whatever your life is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- schools, of course, were not permitted in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a lot of private instruction and group instruction going on, and many teachers, of course.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
